column4: 熔点低，具有一定的机械强度，良好的导电性能，抗腐蚀性能好，附着力强  Low melting point, mechanical strength, good electrical conductivity, good corrosion resistance and strong adhesion
column5: 主要用于半导体材料，电子元器件，电气系统，航空通讯系统，导航通讯系统等制造用材料、焊接、钎焊和低温焊接材料。  It is mainly used in semiconductor materials, electronic components, electrical system, aviation communication system, navigation communication system and other manufacturing materials, welding, brazing and low temperature welding materials.
